हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description:
A young woman discovers the man she secretly loved is about to marry someone else. Unable to bear the pain, she crashes his wedding to confess the love she never dared to express.
This is a tender, bittersweet tale of heartbreak, courage, and a last desperate attempt to win a lost love.
